  <brief_title>Right Ventricular Hypertrophy and Pulmonary Hypertension: A Correlation Analysis</brief_title>
  <official_title>Right Ventricular Hypertrophy and Pulmonary Hypertension: A Correlation Analysis Between Tc-99m Tetrofosmin SPECT Adn Echocardiography</official_title>
